aim_constructionX: Lamda Rising - Tutorials, Mapping and more.URL

_sText: Aim_constructionX is a little aim_map for (max)16 Players. There are 2 floors with many boxes where you can hide, two sideways, 4 doors to the middle and much more. Following weapons are included: m4a1, AK47, Famas, Galil, mp5, HE and one m249.
